title: USA to ban China's Xinjiang cotton import. Know more about it's impact on India.
US blocks Xinjiang cotton imports over Uyghur 'slave labour'
Legislation prohibiting product imports containing cotton grown in the Xinjiang region of China.
description: China is, by far, the largest exporter of cotton apparel to the U.S. Over 85% of the cotton grown in China comes from Xinjiang.
